Feature: Morsmordre (Dark Mark)

    Conjures the Dark Mark, Voldemort's mark. It is often used to mark deaths,
    or cause terror (as at the Quidditch World Cup in The Goblet of Fire)

    Pronunciation:
        /mɔrzˈmɔrdrə/ morz-MOR-drə
    Seen/mentioned:
        Used by Barty Crouch Jr in Goblet of Fire. Also seen in Half-Blood
        Prince over the castle to lure Dumbledore to his death. Voldemort
        apparently invented it. According to Mr. Weasley, very few wizards know
        how to cast this spell.
